name: Kenneth Hopel
text: I hope new people are running this place because 14 years ago the right hand didn’t know what the left hand was doing.

name: Brittany
text: Easy to find, workers seemed lazy, just riding around on forklifts having to ask what to do next, even with trucks docked obviously waiting to be unloaded, we arrived around 7:20am and wasnt finished unloading until 9:30am. Dont be in a rush here, we pulled up right b4 another truck & he had a shorter trailer so while we was pulling up to back on the dock he cut around us & got docked, so even though we were first getting here since he beat us to the dock they started on him immediately, but when it came to us, it took abt 30 mins after he left for them to even start on us, that didnt seem fair, they knew we was there first but started him b4 us because he was local. We will be avoiding this place next time!

name: Kiami Sue
text: Friendly and quick and tidy unloading
